author: eTN Global Editor
title: Air Lease Corporation leases 737-800 to new customer in Asia
text:
Air Lease Corporation leases 737-800 to new customer in Asia Adv: 
Jul 16, 2015 Adv: 
LOS ANGELES, CA - Air Lease Corporation announced a long term lease agreement with Far Eastern Air Transport (FEAT), an international airline based in Taipei, Taiwan, for one new Boeing 737-800. The aircraft is from ALC’s order book with Boeing and will deliver in the second quarter of 2016. 
“ALC is very pleased to lease the first new 737-800 to Far Eastern Air Transport and add them as a new customer in Asia. We look forward to a long and supportive relationship as they begin to renew and expand their fleet,” said Steven F. Udvar-Házy, Air Lease Corporation’s Chairman and Chief Executive Officer.
